{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"}],"title":"setUserId:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a unique user ID with the device to:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Track users across multiple devices"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable user-based targeting in campaigns"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link push engagement to user accounts in your analytics"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support user migration between devices"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Set user ID after successful login:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class AuthenticationService {","","    func handleSuccessfulLogin(user: User) {","        \/\/ Set user ID for cross-device tracking","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","","        \/\/ Set email if available","        if let email = user.email {","            Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Update user profile tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"logged_in\": true,","            \"login_date\": Date(),","            \"login_count\": incrementLoginCount(),","            \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"subscription_status\": user.subscription?.status.rawValue ?? \"none\"","        ])","","        \/\/ Sync with analytics platforms","        Analytics.identify(user.id, traits: [","            \"email\": user.email ?? \"\",","            \"pushwoosh_hwid\": Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","        ])","","        Logger.info(\"User logged in: \\(user.id)\")","    }","","    func handleAccountDeletion() {","        \/\/ Clear user identity","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(\"\")","","        \/\/ Clear all user data tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"logged_in\": false,","            \"user_id\": NSNull(),","            \"email\": NSNull(),","            \"account_deleted\": true,","            \"deletion_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Unregister from push","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { _ in }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier for the current device.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:":{"title":"setUserId:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier for the current device."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:"}}}